既女人打車輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想合嘗 女人嘴內香氣同煙臭味混合<br />\n<br />\n同變性人做愛都想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T00:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8422aa1a3fbe2906d728f29b2170c5ffef64dddb","tid":2290193,"uid":349955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"肥撚到成座山咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48b44ed18cc31b838d8831f6a766a7cecaecba8","tid":2290193,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有生之年要試埋比男人拮</blockquote>sor,呢個<span class=\"x-large\">堅</span>接受唔到<br />\n但比人妖拮有小小想試</blockquote>"},{"pid":"34b6581741b26f0d3daa902a9cdbd94dd5be3ac1","tid":2290193,"uid":33441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"你都食得幾偏喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76504d1ce0eb5cb2be3da9d60cf66716a81055cb","tid":2290193,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:05:30.000Z","msg":"坦"},{"pid":"0374e35757346cea3d6507052a750977054756a7","tid":2290193,"uid":122217,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"大部份肥到成座山咁嘅肥婆，條頸後面都好多老泥，因為佢哋沖涼嘅時候卒唔到。 <br />\n<br />\n老泥俾頸部脂肪一層層夾住，日復日年復年咁累積。 <br />\n所以大部份肥婆條頸都係黑色，越黑老泥越厚。 <br />\n如果你哋有幸溝到肥婆，就人一世物一世點都要試下。<br />\n首先用手指濕少少水起勢咁卒，用匙羹刮出嚟，加兩滴美極慢慢品嚐。 <br />\n初哥可能話核突，但你唔食肥婆老泥等於登上白雲山唔食山水豆腐花一樣咁傻的嗎。 <br />\n<br />\n下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。 <br />\n所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。 <br />\n據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。 <br />\n所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。 <br />\n奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。 <br />\n陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。<br />\n奶嗰時攝攝聲，有3D立體音響加回音效果。 <br />\n你嗅覺，味覺，觸覺，聽覺得到前所未有嘅享受，呢啲先叫人生啊。 <br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪嗰part唔多講，因為肥婆塊田多肉好撞係常識，你塞咗入去會感受到溫暖同安全感，比一層一層肉緊緊包住。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日笑肥婆以為自己好識食嗰啲人，根本就係未夠班，自以為是嘅表現。你比食女界嘅高手揀減肥前欣宜定係整容後楊怡，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},{"pid":"dea6eaecdbc38086a0e59942f443165304461429","tid":2290193,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iz9pbYK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz9pbYK.gif&h=96fafce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HiDmeb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiDmeb5.png&h=f3f6e908&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"436287a95d6ed698f373c4377835c38d54781bea","tid":2290193,"uid":116714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eccc4719151f21e6d31b03e35bb1378617a6d0b2","tid":2290193,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68923fe91b14ef3c3c58becdf851c3792e537b10","tid":2290193,"uid":183576,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T00:25:41.000Z","msg":"大佬你唔好咁痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"咁每個人都有夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔追夢白活一生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:08:26.000Z","msg":"怕你從此多咗個惡夢，見肥少少既女人都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b1aa5161814bdb82276af7d84912bdf544b1f3","tid":2290193,"uid":176981,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:09:13.000Z","msg":"Catgirl 啱啱分左手，樓主機會黎啦"},{"pid":"f233ce766e7695b5cba5afb73f1ca565adb89dfa","tid":2290193,"uid":45173,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-